{"tid":2149653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：據了解國安法沒追溯期 既往不咎","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T03:39:42.000Z","uid":70964,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5bdd3e8bb6d3697c45d4702984c6a2e3566109","tid":2149653,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】「港區國安法」日前公布草案說明，但無公布具體內容，行政長官林鄭月娥昨晨稱，港區國安法未提及追溯期，照她了解，「就是既往不咎，由生效日起才執行」。被問到支持港區國安法會否成為參選「入閘」資格，她說「無感覺到」法例內容意圖增加參選人條件。香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒認為，現時無法律條文，林鄭月娥僅是意圖降溫「出口術」，稱法例通過後自然會秋後算帳。"},{"pid":"1b4c23f199a042af70a09a2c1a67482cff15938c","tid":2149653,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429818e23e62174e6ebe897c83dba579983e4c87","tid":2149653,"uid":165136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"聽日就話<br />\n吖唔好意思，我理解錯咗，原來有㗎？"},{"pid":"cb646f01e1c3717635823e0efb757ecd92f17228","tid":2149653,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429818e23e62174e6ebe897c83dba579983e4c87","tid":2149653,"uid":165136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"聽日就話<br />\n吖唔好意思，我理解錯咗，原來有㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"203d2a0f8aa79556a4b1dc9e87ddf7831fba5553","tid":2149653,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429818e23e62174e6ebe897c83dba579983e4c87","tid":2149653,"uid":165136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"聽日就話<br />\n吖唔好意思，我理解錯咗，原來有㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"林奠都係呃9人"},{"pid":"113c4f646c95a94465397ef04e64038a0b14ce56","tid":2149653,"uid":89608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"據佢了解姐, <br />\n佢了解錯左囉, SOR 囉"},{"pid":"be67419fef68434e47c8a553d9f6a057cdef13ee","tid":2149653,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"113c4